Package fun.ccmc.jmplib

Class SkullCreator

java.lang.Object
fun.ccmc.jmplib.SkullCreator
public class SkullCreator
extends Object
A library for the Bukkit API to create player skulls from names, base64 strings, and texture URLs. Does not use any NMS code, and should work across all versions.
Author:
Dean B on 12/28/2016.
